.TH LIGHTNING-PEER-CHANNEL-COUNT-SKEWNESS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-channel-count-skewness \- skewness of channel counts per peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning peer-channel-count-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the skewness of the channel count distribution across peers.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key channel_count_skewness_peer.
